      "description": "Get ready for a reliable daily driver that's perfect for anyone seeking great value! This vehicle is in solid working order and ready to hit the road. While it shows some honest signs of use and typical cosmetic wear, it remains a dependable choice that gets the job done without breaking the bank. A fantastic opportunity to own a functional car at a very accessible price!",
