      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, currently held in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. Meticulously preserved and maintained to the highest standards, this specimen exhibits no discernible wear, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. From the unblemished exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, every detail confirms its status as a premier example of the marque. Performance is as refined as its aesthetic, offering a driving experience that remains indistinguishable from new.",
